\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::0>[[ Evan grabs the vintage doll from his car and hands it to Sarah. The typically stoic Sarah is giddy like a schoolgirl upon receiving her gift from Evan. Tears even came to her eyes as she remembered the sentimental nature of the gift \endash  the pendant she was wearing today. The pendant cannot be seen because she's worried it will get damaged, so it's tucked under her sweatshirt. ]]<!$Scr_Cs::0>}
