\par\plain {\f0\fs28\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1>Sarah: <!$Scr_Cs::1>}{\f0\fs28\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I'm nervous but as ready as I'll ever be.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::0>[[ Evan gives her a reassuring hug and tells her not to worry.]]}
\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b0\i1\cf4 [[ Sarah opens her car door and grabs a book. ]]}
\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b0\i1\cf4 Sarah: "Evan, do you mind if I read a book during your game?"}
\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b0\i1\cf4 [[ Evan smiles warmly and supportively. ]]<!$Scr_Cs::0>}
\par\plain {\f0\fs28\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1>Evan: <!$Scr_Cs::1>}{\f0\fs28\b0\i0 "Of course, I don't mind. Our games can last as long as two hours, and I fully support and understand that your academics are your number one priority. I'm nothing but grateful that you're coming to my games. I know we just met, but for some reason, it feels like such an important thing. So yes, schoolbook and study material you need for any game."}
\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::0>[[ Sarah laughs, as she knows that Evan is unaware of the book\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8217\'92s title. This leads to a funny and sweet moment. ]]}
\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b0\i1\cf4 [[ Sarah giggles. She feigns seriousness. ]]<!$Scr_Cs::0>}
\par\plain {\f0\fs28\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1>Sarah:<!$Scr_Cs::1>}{\f0\fs28\b0\i0  "That's good to know; maybe I'll need to bring some study materials one day. But this book is not about academics.\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::0>[[ She smiled widely and showed Evan the front of the book. It's titled Softball for Dummies. }
\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b0\i1\cf4 This causes a hearty laugh from both Sarah and Evan.  ]]<!$Scr_Cs::0>}
\par\plain {\f0\fs28\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1>Sarah:<!$Scr_Cs::1>}{\f0\fs28\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I don't know anything about sports. If I'm going to come to games, I want to understand them as best as I can.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs28\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1>Evan:<!$Scr_Cs::1>}{\f0\fs28\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You are so adorable!\u8221\'94 }
\par\plain {\f2\fs28\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::0>[[ Sarah has never been called adorable by anyone. Endorphins flow. ]]<!$Scr_Cs::0>}
\par\plain {\f0\fs28\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1>Evan:<!$Scr_Cs::1>}{\f0\fs28\b0\i0  "The game is about to start. Let\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s go."}
